snippet.title: ZX Spectrum Walkthrough - 3D Starstrike
snippet.description: Walkthrough for the ZX Spectrum game 3D Starstrike. A really playable game with fast colourful 3D wire-frame graphics, it plays like the Star Wars game. Shoot the spaceships, travel across the planet shooting the towers, then through the catwalk to finally bomb the vents.
